Welcome to our store! Product Index below

%p

%table
  %th Product Name
  %th Product Description
  %th Product Price
  - @products.each do |product|
    %tr
      %td
        = link_to product.name, product_path(product)
      %td
        = product.description
      %td
        = form_tag add_item_cart_path do
          = hidden_field_tag 'product_id', product.id
          = submit_tag "Buy!"